SKILL|gif-search|"Search/download GIFs from Tenor via curl + jq."
STEP|1|`curl` and `jq` (both standard on macOS/Linux)
STEP|2|`TENOR_API_KEY` environment variable
STEP|3|URL-encode the query: spaces as `+`, special chars as `%XX`
STEP|4|For sending in chat, `tinygif` URLs are lighter weight
STEP|5|GIF URLs can be used directly in markdown: `![alt](url)`
PIT|URL-encode the query: spaces as `+`, special chars as `%XX`
